This is the key discipline: the layout does not invent state, it renders it.

5) services/people_group_service.py, ensure API returns stable, deterministic paths

The skip bug is mostly your signature, but you should also make group results deterministic so the UI is stable.

In your function that returns matching photos for a group (log shows Together matches for group X), ensure your SQL ends with an order:

ORDER BY created_ts ASC, path ASC (or created_date, then path)

So any time you compute results, the returned list is stable.

